summary: I watched 10 episodes of the Star Wars Attack of the Clones yesterday and 2 today and I am exited. I’m in live with clones....
body: I watched 10 episodes of the Star Wars Attack of the Clones yesterday and 2 today and I am exited. I’m in live with clones. Expecially Rex and Cody. There will be 6 seasons before order 66, so it would be great to watch how clones work with Obi Wan and Anakin and Jedi in general. I love Asoka too~

summary:
Star Wars Adventures: Destroyer Down #1 Publisher: IDW Publishing 





(W) Scott Beatty (A/CA) Jon Sommariva (A/CA) Derek...
caption:
Star Wars Adventures: Destroyer Down #1

Publisher: IDW Publishing
(W) Scott Beatty (A/CA) Jon Sommariva (A/CA) Derek Charm

Swallowed by the shifting sands of Jakku, the Imperial Star Destroyer Spectral has been lost for two decades, giving rise to rumors of hauntings and buried treasure. But an epic sandstorm has revealed the ruins of the starship, and renowned scavenger Rey now leads the race to claim whatever lies within!

Three-issue mini-series set during the days before The Force Awakens!
Includes a backup story depicting the Battle of Jakku, revealing how the Star Destroyer Spectral met its fate during the last days of the Empire!

In Shops: Nov 07, 2018
